quran[7{c,v,t}:
16,73,aur Allah ko chore kar unn ko pujte hain jin ke haath mein nah asmano se inhen kuch bhi rizaq dena hai nah zameen se aur nah yeh kaam woh kar hi satke hain ?
16,74,"pas Allah ke liye misalein nah gharo, Allah jaanta hai, tum nahi jantay"
16,75,"Allah aik misaal deta hai aik to hai ghulam, jo dosray ka mamlook hai aur khud koi ikhtiyar nahi rakhta dosra shakhs aisa hai jisay hum ne apni taraf se acha rizaq ataa kya hai aur woh is mein se khulay aur chupay khoob kharch karta hai batao, kya yeh dono barabar hain?sab khobyan Akllah ko hai, magar aksar log ( is seedhi baat ko ) nahi jantay"
16,76,"Allah aik aur misaal deta hai do aadmi hain aik goonga berha hai, koi kaam nahi kar sakta, apne aaqa par boojh bana howa hai, jidhar bhi woh usay beje koi bhala kaam uss se ban nah aeye dosra shakhs aisa hai ke insaaf ka hukum deta hai aur khud raah raast par qaim hai batao kya yeh dono yaksaa hain ?"
16,77,"aur zameen o aasman ke posheeda haqayiq ka ilm to Allah hi ko hai aur qayamat ke barpaa honay ka maamla kuch der nah le ga magar bas itni ke jis mein aadmi ki palak jhapak jaye, balkay is se bhi kuch kam haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah sab kuch kar sakta hai"
16,78,"Allah ne tum ko tumhari maaon ke piton se nikala is haalat mein ke tum kuch nah jantay thay uss ne tumhe kaan diye, ankhen den, aur sochnay walay dil diye, is liye ke tum shukar guzaar bano"
16,79,kya inn logon ne kabhi parindon ko nahi dekha ke fazayaasmani mein kisi terhan maskhar hain? Allah ke siwa kis ne inn ko thaam rakha hai? iss mein bohat nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo imaan laatay hain
